{"word":"Cherubim","slug":"cherubim","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Cherubim</b> Eastward of the garden of Eden<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=24'>Gen 3:24</a><br/> In the tabernacle<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=25&verse=20'>Exo 25:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=37&verse=9'>Exo 37:9</a> <br/> - Ark rested beneath the wings of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8&verse=7'>1Ki 8:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=5&verse=8'>2Ch 5:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse=5'>Heb 9:5</a> <br/> - Figures of, embroidered:<br/> b on walls of tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=26&verse=1'>Exo 26:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=36&verse=8'>Exo 36:8</a><br/> b on the vail<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=26&verse=31'>Exo 26:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=36&verse=35'>Exo 36:35</a><br/> In the temple<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=6&verse=29'>1Ki 6:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=3&verse=13'>2Ch 3:13</a> <br/> - Figures of:<br/> b on the vail<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=3&verse=14'>2Ch 3:14</a><br/> b on the walls<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=6&verse=35'>1Ki 6:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=3&verse=7'>2Ch 3:7</a><br/> b on the lavers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=29'>1Ki 7:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=36'>1Ki 7:36</a><br/> In Ezekiel's vision of the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=41&